<p rend="chapter">Pāṭihāriyadīpanīgāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="175"><hi rend="paranum">175</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Brahmassa saddaṃ karavīkabhāṇiṃ,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Yathicchitaṃ sāvayituṃ samatthaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Saccaṃ piyaṃ bhūtahitaṃ vadantaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Na pūjaye ko hi naro sacetano.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="176"><hi rend="paranum">176</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Iddhi ca ādesanānusāsanī,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Pāṭihīre bhagavā vasī ahu;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Katvāna accherasupāṭihīraṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Desesi dhammaṃ anukampimaṃ pajaṃ.</p>
</body>
